OL,3,CPlaid's childcare offer to happen
OL,4,C'quickly' but no timetable confirmed
OL,6,FThe First Minister said his promise to
OL,7,Fexpand free childcare will happen
OL,8,F"very quickly" but declined to confirm
OL,9,Fa timetable of implementation.
OL,11,FRhun ap Iorwerth made his first visit
OL,12,Fin the top job to a childcare provider
OL,13,Fin Merthyr Tydfil on Wednesday (20
OL,14,FMay) in order to highlight Plaid
OL,15,FCymru's promise of 20 hours of funded
OL,16,Fcare for all children aged between
OL,17,Fnine months and four years old.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@NO]
