OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1779447783
OL,3,CPlaid's childcare offer to happen
OL,4,C'quickly' but no timetable confirmed
OL,6,FThe pledge is for full roll-out within
OL,7,Ffour years, but the First Minister
OL,8,Frefused to say exactly when the
OL,9,Fexpansion would begin.
OL,11,FMr ap Iorwerth told ITV Cymru Wales:
OL,12,F"What we have already started to do is
OL,13,Fget to grips with the work of building
OL,14,Fup to what will be a sustained rollout
OL,15,Fof a childcare offer that will
OL,16,Ftransform lives.
OL,18,F"Elements have begun already, other
OL,19,Felements - building up the workforce,
OL,20,Ffor example - will take slightly
OL,21,Flonger but this is worth the graft."
OL,26,@tD@AOUzD@AOU}D@dO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
