FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1779447783
OL,3,CPlaid's childcare offer to happen
OL,4,C'quickly' but no timetable confirmed
OL,6,FWhen asked if it would begin by the
OL,7,Fend of the year, the First Minister
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are looking to do that very,
OL,9,Fvery, very quickly. But there are
OL,10,Felements then in terms of building a
OL,11,Fworkforce, aligning the funding, to
OL,12,Fdeliver it at full rollout that I
OL,13,Fthink people expect, will take, a
OL,14,Flittle bit longer because this has to
OL,15,Fbe sustainable.
OL,17,F"We're not doing something here, you
OL,18,Fknow, as a quick win.
OL,26,@pD@GOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
