OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1779447783
OL,3,CPlaid's childcare offer to happen
OL,4,C'quickly' but no timetable confirmed
OL,6,F"We are doing something which is a
OL,7,Fsustainable win for families and
OL,8,Fcommunities the length and breadth of
OL,9,FWales for many years to come. We've
OL,10,Fgot to get this right."
OL,12,FRhun ap Iorwerth's government want to
OL,13,Fphase in the 20 funded hours offer and
OL,14,Fsaid it would apply to 48 weeks of the
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FThey also plan to maintain the
OL,18,Fprevious government's offer of 30
OL,19,Fhours of funded childcare for children
OL,20,Faged three to four whose parents are
OL,21,Fin work, education, or training.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@WO]
