OL,3,CPlaid's childcare offer to happen
OL,4,C'quickly' but no timetable confirmed
OL,6,FWelsh language provision will also be
OL,7,Fexpanded under the Welsh Government
OL,8,Fplans.
OL,10,FThe Deputy First Minister, whose remit
OL,11,Fincludes childcare policy, added:
OL,12,F"Thousands of parents in Wales are
OL,13,Fworking solely to cover the cost of
OL,14,Fchildcare, and many cannot afford it
OL,15,Fat all. This needs to change.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/10
