PN,46706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1779447783
OL,3,CPlaid's childcare offer to happen
OL,4,C'quickly' but no timetable confirmed
OL,6,F"Access to affordable childcare
OL,7,Funlocks opportunities and gives
OL,8,Fparents, especially mothers, the
OL,9,Ffreedom to return to work, education
OL,10,For training. And most importantly, our
OL,11,Fexpanded offer of high-quality
OL,12,Fchildcare will give every child the
OL,13,Fhead-start they need to thrive."
OL,15,FCommenting, Reform Wales said: "Reform
OL,16,Fsupports the principle of supporting
OL,17,Fparents and families with financial
OL,18,Frelief to help with the cost-of-living.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@`O]wD@`OU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/10
