PN,46707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1779447783
OL,3,CPlaid's childcare offer to happen
OL,4,C'quickly' but no timetable confirmed
OL,6,F"We proposed an ambitious and costed
OL,7,Ftax cutting programme for working
OL,8,Fpeople to achieve this.
OL,10,F"Plaid must be clear how they intend
OL,11,Fto fund their commitments, given they
OL,12,Fare incredibly expensive and have
OL,13,Fclearly not yet been costed."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@]O]
