OL,3,CPlaid's childcare offer to happen
OL,4,C'quickly' but no timetable confirmed
OL,6,FWelsh Labour's spokesperson for
OL,7,FChildren, Education, and Lifelong
OL,8,FLearning, Lynne Neagle MS said: "We
OL,9,Fall want to see a fantastic childcare
OL,10,Foffer for families in Wales. But in
OL,11,Fgovernment, you must balance
OL,12,Fpriorities and budgets. Wales is right
OL,13,Fto expect serious government from the
OL,14,FSenedd. And serious government means
OL,15,Fbeing honest, being clear, and showing
OL,16,Fthe sums.
OL,18,F"Will it be the schools budget that is
OL,19,Fcut to fund childcare? Will it be
OL,20,Fhealthcare?"
OL,26,@pD@aOUzD@AOU|D@LO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/10
