PN,46709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1779447783
OL,3,CPlaid's childcare offer to happen
OL,4,C'quickly' but no timetable confirmed
OL,6,FCommenting, Welsh Conservative Shadow
OL,7,FCabinet Minister for Education,
OL,8,FFamilies and Constitution, Sam
OL,9,FRowlands MS said the principle of
OL,10,Fimproving childcare is "important and
OL,11,F"can provide support," but that Plaid
OL,12,Fneeds to be "honest about how it will
OL,13,Fbe funded."
OL,15,FHe said: "The Deputy First Minister's
OL,16,Fcomments in an ITV interview that
OL,17,FPlaid have not yet begun planning how
OL,18,Fthis will be fully delivered are
OL,19,Fextremely concerning.
OL,26,@wD@JOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/10
