PN,46710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1779447783
OL,3,CPlaid's childcare offer to happen
OL,4,C'quickly' but no timetable confirmed
OL,6,F"The Welsh Conservatives believe that
OL,7,Fany funding for this policy must not
OL,8,Fcome from cuts to essential services.
OL,9,FWith Plaid already talking about
OL,10,Fdiverting money away from health into
OL,11,Fsports and arts, it is deeply
OL,12,Fconcerning that frontline services
OL,13,Fcould be put at risk to fund their
OL,14,Funcosted promises."
